<paragraph base="F45929918" id="IFRS16_B5"><paranum>B5</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="B5"/></prolog><body><p outputclass="keep_with_next" id="IFRS16_P0419">An <xref base="F45929849" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0392">underlying asset<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0373"/></ph></xref> can be of low value only if:</p><ol base="F45929920" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS16_L0042"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F45929921" id="IFRS16_P0420">the <xref base="F45929736" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0380">lessee<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0220"/></ph></xref> can benefit from use of the underlying asset on its own or together with other resources that are readily available to the lessee; and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F45929923" id="IFRS16_P0421">the underlying asset is not highly dependent on, or highly interrelated with, other assets.</p>       </li></ol></body></paragraph>